# Project Structure Guide

This React Native + Expo project's key entry points are:

- [app/\_layout.tsx](mdc:app/_layout.tsx) – sets up global providers and navigation.
- [app/index.tsx](mdc:app/index.tsx) – the main screen containing the interactive drawing canvas.

Supporting files/directories:

- Static assets live in [assets/](mdc:assets/)
- Database utilities: [db.ts](mdc:db.ts)
- Expo & Metro configuration at the repo root (e.g. [app.json](mdc:app.json), [metro.config.js](mdc:metro.config.js)).

This rule gives future AI assistants a quick roadmap of where to start when exploring the codebase.
